title: PLANET OF THE APES CATACLYSM 01-06, 09-10, BETRAYAL 01-04
description:
14 Planet of the Apes issues from Boom, most of which haven't been posted on TPB.

Here are 8 issues of Planet of the Apes: Cataclysm, which is an ongoing series I think. I couldn't find 07, 08, which should be -- but perhaps haven't been -- scanned, or 11, which came out this month. And I searched! But if you can scan them, or find the scans, post them you damn, dirty ape!

Also, Betrayal of the Planet of the Apes miniseries 01-04 complete.

Planet of the Apes Special 01, which came out recently.

and last but not least, from back in 2011, Rise of the Planet of the Apes Prequel, which was posted here but wasn't seeded anymore.

Don't go bananas, please seed and enjoy!  --STF
